    <body>
        <p>If you have a termbase file in Lingo, you can export it into a Translation Memory eXchange (TMX) file to share with others or to save for later. To do this, select the database in the grid, then click <span class="Emphasis">Export</span>. Complete the fields in the dialog and click <span class="Emphasis">Start Export</span>.</p>
    </body>
</html>